relation: Darrow1 - #77 WHOOOOOOOOOOA!! A shocking development! Mr. Saturn has finally arrived! More exclamation points!!!!

Darrow1 - #78 Ness and friends decide to help the Mr. Saturn, but first, a stop off at the local store. Unfortunately for Ness, even if he did fill his inventory with Peanut Cheese Bars, Reginald would just eat them all.
